00:27:45,334 --> 00:27:47,302
-Hit it!
-Hit it!

271
00:27:49,634 --> 00:27:51,968
He promised to tell his
wife in two months...

272
00:27:52,234 --> 00:27:54,367
...and get a divorce.

273
00:27:55,968 --> 00:28:00,135
If you embrace them
with a generous heart...

274
00:28:00,234 --> 00:28:02,568
...they will come to their senses one day.

275
00:28:05,534 --> 00:28:07,567
We're not just fooling around.

276
00:28:08,033 --> 00:28:10,333
He's been serious since
we've met two years ago.

277
00:28:10,434 --> 00:28:14,402
Home run! Run! Run!

278
00:28:14,501 --> 00:28:17,534
- Okay!
- Yes!

279
00:28:22,300 --> 00:28:23,433
Nice!

280
00:28:25,868 --> 00:28:27,235
You and Joonyoung...

281
00:28:28,033 --> 00:28:31,734
...mean everything to Taeoh.

282
00:28:38,767 --> 00:28:40,468
Okay! One more!

283
00:28:42,734 --> 00:28:44,635
Have you made your decision?

284
00:28:47,834 --> 00:28:49,702
Have you made your decision?

285
00:28:52,968 --> 00:28:56,502
First... Check his financial situation.

286
00:29:05,968 --> 00:29:07,502
Long time no see, ma'am.

287
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:15,334
(Financial Transaction Records)

288
00:29:15,434 --> 00:29:19,201
Your husband always came by without you.

289
00:29:19,667 --> 00:29:21,268
Have you been busy at work?

290
00:29:21,734 --> 00:29:24,034
I'm going to make time
to come by from now on.

291
00:29:24,334 --> 00:29:26,901
I feel bad for leaving everything
up to my husband.

292
00:29:27,601 --> 00:29:32,035
You cannot let your husband know
until you confirm everything.

293
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:34,901
Act natural as if nothing happened.

294
00:29:35,334 --> 00:29:36,202
Okay?

295
00:29:36,267 --> 00:29:40,768
After we moved your bank accounts
to your husband's company name,

296
00:29:41,801 --> 00:29:44,335
there's nothing to settle.

297
00:29:46,167 --> 00:29:49,300
But you are behind on interest payments.

298
00:29:51,133 --> 00:29:51,900
What?

299
00:29:54,234 --> 00:29:55,768
I mean...

300
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:58,834
...the interest from the mortgage loan.

301
00:30:00,767 --> 00:30:02,201
It's been overdue for
four months now.

302
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:04,534
I thought you came by to settle that.

303
00:30:11,934 --> 00:30:15,168
He got a mortgage loan?

304
00:30:17,467 --> 00:30:18,534
When?

305
00:30:21,434 --> 00:30:23,467
It's already been three years.

306
00:30:25,100 --> 00:30:26,801
He said you were busy,

307
00:30:26,868 --> 00:30:30,135
so he brought a seal and the
power of attorney....

308
00:30:30,234 --> 00:30:31,801
...to process the mortgage request.

309
00:30:33,534 --> 00:30:35,634
That process is illegal now,

310
00:30:35,834 --> 00:30:39,168
but a power of attorney was
enough back then.

311
00:30:41,267 --> 00:30:44,868
He said he already discussed
all the details with you.

312
00:30:45,334 --> 00:30:46,868
So we processed the request.

313
00:30:46,934 --> 00:30:50,134
No wonder he looked so
tormented these days.

314
00:30:52,067 --> 00:30:53,668
Now I know why.

315
00:30:55,701 --> 00:30:58,035
I guess he couldn't tell me
because he felt guilty.

316
00:30:58,133 --> 00:30:59,800
I see.

317
00:31:04,234 --> 00:31:05,102
Is there...

318
00:31:06,067 --> 00:31:09,100
...anything else I need to know?

319
00:31:13,934 --> 00:31:16,301
I don't want it to become
a problem later on.

320
00:31:17,667 --> 00:31:18,967
Please tell me.

321
00:31:22,767 --> 00:31:24,635
He got a premium loan...

322
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:28,300
...using your son's
variable life insurance.

323
00:31:29,300 --> 00:31:30,934
You didn't know?

324
00:32:21,901 --> 00:32:23,168
(Gosan Bank, Mr. Lee Taeoh)

325
00:32:23,267 --> 00:32:25,101
(Balance : 9,850 won)

326
00:32:26,634 --> 00:32:29,268
(Joeun Bank Savings Account,
Mr. Lee Taeoh)

327
00:32:29,334 --> 00:32:31,868
(Balance: 11,290 won)

328
00:32:31,968 --> 00:32:33,902
(Gosan Bank Checking Account)

329
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:35,601
(Balance: 7,930 won)

330
00:33:14,300 --> 00:33:16,867
